- Initial Inspection
    - Helps us to just preview the data and understand the data types of the columns

- Data Cleaning
    - Helps us to clean the data by removing duplicates, handling missing values, etc

- Univariate Analysis(It involves using chart visualization)
    - Helps us to understand the distribution of the data in each column, basically
       we shall be able to detect the anomalies or patterns in the data

- Bivariate / Multivariate Analysis(It also involves using chart visualization)
    - Helps us to understand the relationship between two variables
    - We can use heatmaps, pairplots, etc

- Advanced Visualizations
    - We can use a violin plot, etc